Package: scrnaExplorer
Type: Project
Title: Modular scRNA-seq Exploration App (R/Shiny)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("scRNA Explorer", "Contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: An R/Shiny application providing modular exploration of
    single-cell RNA-seq data. Not a CRAN/Bioconductor package; the
    DESCRIPTION exists so that standard R tooling (testthat, R CMD check,
    devtools::test, IDE support) can manage dependencies and run tests.
